pig track
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a track formed on rough hill country or through bush by a wild pig.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka pig-track
